	<key>readme</key>
	<string>## Prompteria Alfred Workflow

Search and copy prompts from your Prompteria library.

### Usage

**Search:** Type `prompts` to search, then ↩ to copy selected prompt to clipboard.

**Add:** Type `add-prompt` to add clipboard content as a new prompt (prompts for title, description, folder; uses Inbox if no folder specified).

### Requirements

- [Prompteria](https://github.com/fortin/prompteria) app installed with prompts created
- Alfred 5 with Powerpack</string>
